snippet.title: DOKDO by Zzoo [Android/iOS] Gameplay ᴴᴰ
snippet.description:
DOKDO by Zzoo is an Relaxing game! Go fishing, upgrade your ship.Go battling! Explore!exotic islands and RULE them!Make this world YOURS!

DOKDO by Zzoo Feature:
◆ Arena : endless battles
◆ Two world maps
◆ Beautiful 3D graphics
◆ Easy to play and control
◆ Compete with your friends

Addictive strategy ocean Game “DOKDO”

Enjoy the addictive “DOKDO” while commuting to work, in the bus or subway, waiting at the bank.

Whenever, wherever “dokdo” is ready for action !!!
Thank you!

Thanks for every Like and Favorite! They really help!
